{"tid":307001,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解大快活個雞胸整得咁嫩","createTime":"2017-07-03T04:18:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T08:58:30.000Z","uid":105970,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1de324d74b839b9e14f765c46fe8ea9d99328934","tid":307001,"uid":105970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:18:21.000Z","msg":"最近想修下身 買左啲雪藏雞胸雞柳返屋企整<br />\n跟阿減肥達人一休咁白烚<br />\n水滾放雞胸 之後熄火焗八分鐘拎上黎<br />\n口感都係好乾好硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知頭先一試大快活個雞胸飯<br />\n心諗點解雞胸可以整得咁好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n求巴絲指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd9e528cc1c931e169953377603152f6e34695f","tid":307001,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:20:31.000Z","msg":"你一講起又想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23aac15e6ce350fc43f0724d71342bfc6f8989f0","tid":307001,"uid":102096,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:23:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"900091bc8acffe2138e0b841683103a7dfd8a93d","tid":307001,"uid":112583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:27:31.000Z","msg":"煮之前有冇鹽水醃過?"},{"pid":"1560f1ae9945bf3c7bc1ec2f5a18e2202116deba","tid":307001,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:28:04.000Z","msg":"落d咩木瓜粉「喇」下佢<br />\n姐係咩蛋白酶之類掛"},{"pid":"2c9b391c72b7906f843f447e42a73079ad67be4e","tid":307001,"uid":13251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:29:18.000Z","msg":"梳打粉淹過"},{"pid":"4ee8a438aeda535b8d7b2c3f94392b5e4a902dfa","tid":307001,"uid":18117,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:29:22.000Z","msg":"你成舊焗8分鐘緊係鞋啦<br />\n首先舊肉要完全解凍哂 <br />\n切一條條手指尾咁粗<br />\n一定要落少少鹽醃<br />\n水滾落肉計大約45s-60s <br />\n熄火焗多60s<br />\n好食過雞扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c36b4d035001847cb62980b1d43f2cb172c8fc0","tid":307001,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:30:07.000Z","msg":"邊隻雞胸飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"551569236c1e0711350ef2e5ff290fd825b6249c","tid":307001,"uid":105970,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你成舊焗8分鐘緊係鞋啦<br />\n首先舊肉要完全解凍哂 <br />\n切一條條手指尾咁粗<br />\n一定要落少少鹽醃<br />\n水滾落肉計大約45s-60s <br />\n熄火焗多60s<br />\n好食過雞扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54420e99e911817d1cebf4a70168c6c57ef156a","tid":307001,"uid":37631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T04:41:57.000Z","msg":"想好食慢煮啦 營養唔流失又juicy"},{"pid":"b1024867573ee42c7555058ffee0cb6d861a801f","tid":307001,"uid":69275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:15:00.000Z","msg":"醃過架"},{"pid":"f5e668cd9c85163a77b3a41976741805ea9a14b2","tid":307001,"uid":11236,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:17:29.000Z","msg":"自己拎烚雞胸餵狗 (唔好屌 純粹覺得狗糧太多化學劑)<br />\n我水喉水放雞胸 煲到水滾<br />\n以後熄火焗佢一兩分鐘都好滑"},{"pid":"ab386a189b7950418c125b2f3b8a956d2d7ffcab","tid":307001,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T05:55:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2b02b66f547ef259953f66471c40d6dc9fdc647","tid":307001,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T06:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊隻雞胸飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅米飯果隻<br />\n超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭先又食完</blockquote><br />\n我見到宣傳牌啊，望落好健康咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi