e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nd雞落勁多油?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6b0c1760a2981ba102f250c3c05696e2e370eaf","tid":307001,"uid":18117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:39:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>邊隻雞胸飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n山楂汁個個 食過3次有兩係好嫩唔鞋</blockquote><br />\n食過兩次 一次好嫩<br />\n另一次灘到凍哂 勁鞋<br />\n所以都係睇你好唔好采<br />\n撞正岩岩整好係幾好食既"},{"pid":"2b91433dcc945be758ce11f7bb76568d4cf66634","tid":307001,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"個汁撈飯陣味好怪 但係點雞都幾好食 唔知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a501a6e58c3f9aa98582a566c6431e948a3a6dfa","tid":307001,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T08:46:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c9271453cfcc48828458499ef822e784eb4a897","tid":307001,"uid":74848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T09:37:12.000Z","msg":"呢兩個月食左七，八次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}